---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

export const prerender = true;

const city = "Salt Lake City";
const tdsLevel = "350-500 ppm";
---

<Layout
  title="Water Filtration Salt Lake City - Blue Logic Water"
  description="Professional reverse osmosis systems for Salt Lake City homes. Combat Utah's hard water with commercial-grade filtration at half the cost."
>
  <section class="hero-gradient py-20 md:py-24 px-4 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-serif mb-4 text-foreground">
        Water Purification for {city}
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-muted-foreground">
        Professional RO systems designed for Utah's unique water challenges
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-background py-16 md:py-20 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <h2
        class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-center mb-12 text-foreground"
      >
        Understanding {city}'s Water
      </h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">
            {tdsLevel}
          </div>
          <div
            class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-4 text-foreground"
          >
            Total Dissolved Solids (TDS)
          </div>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            Salt Lake City water typically contains high mineral content due to
            mountain runoff and geological factors.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">
            Very Hard
          </div>
          <div
            class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-4 text-foreground"
          >
            Water Hardness Rating
          </div>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            Utah consistently ranks among the hardest water states in the
            nation.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif mb-4 text-foreground">
          What's in Your Water?
        </h3>
        <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Salt Lake City's water supply comes from mountain watersheds and
          underground sources. While generally safe to drink, it contains high
          levels of:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li
            class="py-4 border-b border-border text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed"
          >
            <strong class="text-foreground">Calcium and Magnesium:</strong> The minerals
            that make water "hard"
          </li>
          <li
            class="py-4 border-b border-border text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed"
          >
            <strong class="text-foreground">Chlorine:</strong> Added for disinfection,
            can affect taste
          </li>
          <li
            class="py-4 border-b border-border text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed"
          >
            <strong class="text-foreground">Trace minerals:</strong> Iron, manganese,
            and other naturally occurring elements
          </li>
          <li class="py-4 text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            <strong class="text-foreground">Potential contaminants:</strong> Varying
            levels of PFAS, lead from old pipes, and agricultural runoff
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-card py-16 md:py-20 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <h2
        class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-center mb-12 text-foreground"
      >
        Why Reverse Osmosis for Utah Homes?
      </h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="reason-card">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-primary">
            Eliminates Hard Water
          </h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            RO removes up to 99% of dissolved minerals, eliminating scale buildup on
            fixtures, appliances, and plumbing. No more spotty dishes or clogged
            showerheads.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="reason-card">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-primary">
            Removes Contaminants
          </h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            Beyond minerals, RO removes chlorine, PFAS, heavy metals, and other
            potential contaminants that simple filters can't touch.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="reason-card">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-primary">
            Better for Your Health
          </h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            Pure water means fewer skin irritations, better hydration, and peace
            of mind knowing what's NOT in your water.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="reason-card">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-primary">
            Protects Your Home
          </h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            Prevent costly damage to water heaters, dishwashers, and plumbing
            systems caused by mineral buildup.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-background py-16 md:py-20 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <h2
        class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-center mb-6 text-foreground"
      >
        Local Service for Local Challenges
      </h2>
      <p
        class="text-lg text-muted-foreground text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12 leading-relaxed"
      >
        We live and work in the Wasatch Front. We understand Utah's water
        because it's our water too. Every Blue Logic system is optimized for the
        specific challenges of Salt Lake Valley water quality.
      </p>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-center mb-8 text-foreground">
          Serving the Entire Wasatch Front
        </h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 text-center">
          <span class="py-3 px-4 bg-card rounded-lg text-foreground font-medium"
            >Salt Lake City</span
          >
          <span class="py-3 px-4 bg-card rounded-lg text-foreground font-medium"
            >Park City</span
          >
          <span class="py-3 px-4 bg-card rounded-lg text-foreground font-medium"
            >Draper</span
          >
          <span class="py-3 px-4 bg-card rounded-lg text-foreground font-medium"
            >Sandy</span
          >
          <span class="py-3 px-4 bg-card rounded-lg text-foreground font-medium"
            >Cottonwood Heights</span
          >
          <span class="py-3 px-4 bg-card rounded-lg text-foreground font-medium"
            >Holladay</span
          >
          <span class="py-3 px-4 bg-card rounded-lg text-foreground font-medium"
            >Murray</span
          >
          <span class="py-3 px-4 bg-card rounded-lg text-foreground font-medium"
            >Millcreek</span
          >
          <span class="py-3 px-4 bg-card rounded-lg text-foreground font-medium"
            >South Jordan</span
          >
          <span class="py-3 px-4 bg-card rounded-lg text-foreground font-medium"
            >West Jordan</span
          >
          <span class="py-3 px-4 bg-card rounded-lg text-foreground font-medium"
            >Taylorsville</span
          >
          <span class="py-3 px-4 bg-card rounded-lg text-foreground font-medium"
            >West Valley City</span
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-card py-16 md:py-20 px-4 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif mb-6 text-foreground">
        Trusted by 500+ Wasatch Front Families
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        From downtown Salt Lake to the foothills, local families trust Blue
        Logic for professional water purification at a fair price.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-background py-16 md:py-20 px-4 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif mb-4 text-foreground">
        Get Your Free Salt Lake City Water Quality Assessment
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-muted-foreground mb-8">
        Schedule a free consultation to see exactly what's in your water
      </p>
      <a href="/#contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Schedule Free Consultation</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  @reference "../styles/global.css";
  .stat-card {
    @apply bg-card p-8 rounded-2xl text-center;
  }

  .reason-card {
    @apply bg-background p-8 rounded-2xl;
  }
</style>
